---
title: Sweet Chilli Chicken & Sesame Veggie Toss with Soy Mayo & Peanut Cashew Mix
description: Are you ready to make one amazing dinner? Get the veggies roasted and coated in sesame seeds for a bit of crunch, whip up a mouth-watering soy-mayo to drizzle over the ginger and sweet chilli coated chicken. If that’s all done then on your marks, get set and dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

